      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new fantasy RPG and I want to make sure the character roster feels diverse and not just like the standard tropes. Can you help me brainstorm 5 unique playable character archetypes that are inspired by different real-world ethnic or cultural backgrounds? Don't just give me names, maybe include their general vibe or what kind of combat style they'd be good at so I can see how they'll play.",
